net.jpountz.lz4

Interface LZ4UnknownSizeDecompressor


  • public interface LZ4UnknownSizeDecompressor
    LZ4 decompressor that requires the size of the compressed data to be known.

    Implementations of this class are usually a little slower than those of LZ4Decompressor but do not require the size of the original data to be known.
